name: Wellesley Hills Branch Library
description:
This is the library I worked in today. The windows were open, and there was a breeze the whole time. If you squint your ears, the traffic on Rte 9 and on Washington St sounds like the ocean.

Later in the summer, it won't be as pleasant. There's no air conditioning. The librarian told me that they shut the library down when the indoor temperature hits 90 degrees.
